lead_paragraph: In Lionel Messi, Luis Suarez and Neymar, Arsenal faces the most potent strike force in the game — and a team that will probably be more than halfway to the Champions League quarterfinals after Tuesday's match.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal's Eyes on Strike Trio as Barcelona Comes to Town
